    "body": "Sorry, we don't have a file-based logger anymore. We removed it about 2 years ago because it's not possible to cater to everyone's needs regarding file logging. People usually have a custom setup anyway, for example, if you are using systemd or supervisord, it can handle this for you. If you are using some cloud deployment tool, it wants to be in charge of logging, etc.",
